### Some steps can be followed to take the road to data science:-

1.The first step is to get good at statistics, if possible take up a crash course in statistics.
2.While an advanced degree in computer science is usually preferred, it is not a must. Get hands on knowledge of programming skills in R, Scala and Python
3.Learn Visualization tools such as Tableau, Microsoft Power BI
4.Understanding of Hadoop and Apache Spark is a must
5.Learn the fundamentals of machine learning algorithms
6.Learn the important tools of the trade â€“ R programming, Python, SPSS, Apache Spark, SQL.
